<html lang="en" data-webtui-theme="catppuccin-mocha">
<meta charset="utf-8">
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
</head>
<body>
<div>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div is-="separator" direction-="horizontal"></div>

        <div class="header" box-="double" shear-="both">
            <div class="header">
                <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><h1>ANDREW WALPOLE</h1></span>
            </div>
            <h2>TECH LEAD | FULL-STACK ENGINEER | AWS CERTIFIED EXPERT</h2>
            <div class="header">
            <span class="consultation" is-="badge" variant-="background0">
                <button><a href="mailto:andy.walpole@gmail?subject=Contact from website">Book a consultation</a></button>
            </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div is-="separator" direction-="horizontal"></div>

        <section box-="square" shear-="top">
            <div class="header">
                <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><h1>Get future-ready</h1></span>
            </div>

            <div id="content">
                <p>As a technology leader and engineer, I view programming as a product-centric activity. My expertise
                    encompasses both back-end and front-end development, emphasising serverless, event-driven
                    architecture and
                    systems thinking. On the front-end, I strive for solutions that combine accessibility, usability,
                    and
                    performance. I enthusiastically endorse The Agile Manifesto and the systems thinking and
                    domain-driven
                    approach now prevalent in our industry. Over my career, I’ve played instrumental roles in
                    significant retail
                    tech initiatives including projects for Tesco, Boots, and Sainsbury's.</p>

                <p>Most recently, I guided tech teams for NBrown’s SimplyBe and Castle projects.</p>

            <ul>
                <li>Positioned the fintech project, Castle, to launch with its first customers in January 2026.</li>
                <li>Delivered full platform relaunch of Simply Be in the autumn of 2022; guided three cross-functional
                    squads in creating a React.js/Next.js monorepo from several different repos, resulting in a
                    successful
                    go-live and improvements in platform performance and stability.
                </li>
                <li>The successful work on the “new web” and the Castle project directly lead to a £181m takeover of
                    NBrown
                    in December 2024.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <p>I was also pivotal in creating Elevaate, which secured £600k in funding and won Startup of the Year at
                Retail
                Week Live 2015.</p>

            <p>My experience spans all levels, from infrastructure to the browser</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div is-="separator" direction-="horizontal"></div>

        <section>
            <h1>Services Offered</h1>

            <div is-="separator" direction-="horizontal"></div>

            <section class="grid">
                <article class="grid-item" box-="square" shear-="top">
                    <div class="header">
                        <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"> <h2>Full-Stack Development</h2></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon">
                        <Image
                                src={Development}
                                widths={[50, 100, Development.width]}
                                sizes={`(max-width: 800px) 50px, (max-width: max) 100px`}
                                alt="A description of my image."
                        />
                    </div>
                    <pre>andywalpole@Andys-IMac-5 portfolio % echo <span>"I craft comprehensive web solutions with a focus on user-centric design."</span> >> development.txt</pre>
                </article>
                <article class="grid-item" box-="square" shear-="top">
                    <div class="header">
                        <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><h2>Technical Leadership</h2></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon">
                        <Image
                                src={LeadershipIcon}
                                widths={[100, 200, LeadershipIcon.width]}
                                sizes={`(max-width: 800px) 100px, (max-width: max) 200px`}
                                alt="A description of my image."
                                inferSize="true"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <pre>andywalpole@Andys-IMac-5 portfolio % echo <span>"I have lead multiple teams to deliver high standards in technology projects."</span> >> leadership.txt</pre>
                </article>
                <article class="grid-item" box-="square" shear-="top">
                    <div class="header">
                        <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><h2>AWS Certified Expert</h2></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon">
                <Image
                        src={AWSIcon}
                        widths={[100, 200, AWSIcon.width]}
                        sizes={`(max-width: 800px) 100px, (max-width: max) 200px`}
                        alt="A description of my image."
                        inferSize="true"
                />
                </div>
                    <pre>andywalpole@Andys-IMac-5 portfolio % echo <span>"I design and implement serverless architectures using AWS for efficient integration."</span> >> infrastructure.txt</pre>
                </article>
                <article class="grid-item" box-="square" shear-="top">
                    <div class="header">
                        <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><h2>Frontend Optimization</h2></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon">
                <Image
                        src={Performance}
                        widths={[100, 200, Performance.width]}
                        sizes={`(max-width: 800px) 100px, (max-width: max) 200px`}
                        alt="A description of my image."
                        inferSize="true"
                />
                </div>
                    <pre>andywalpole@Andys-IMac-5 portfolio % echo <span>"I enhance website performance through skilled frontend development practices."</span> >> performance.txt</pre>
                </article>
                <article class="grid-item" box-="square" shear-="top">
                    <div class="header">
                        <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><h2>AI development</h2></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="icon">
                <Image
                        src={AIIcon}
                        widths={[100, 200, AIIcon.width]}
                        sizes={`(max-width: 800px) 100px, (max-width: max) 200px`}
                        alt="A description of my image."
                        inferSize="true"
                />
                </div>
                    <pre>andywalpole@Andys-IMac-5 portfolio % echo <span>"With extensive experience in AI development, I have worked with a wide range of modern tools and frameworks to design, build, and optimize intelligent systems."</span> >> ai.txt</pre>
                </article>
            </section>

        </section>

        <article is-="typography-block">
            <h1>Experience</h1>
        </article>

    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
<style>
    .wrapper {
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2ch;
    }

    p:not(:last-child) {
        margin-bottom: 1lh;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 1lh;
    }

    @layer base {
        :root {
            [data-webtui-theme='catppuccin-*'] {
                /* Accent Colors */
                --rosewater: #f5e0dc;
                --flamingo: #f2cdcd;
                --pink: #f5c2e7;
                --mauve: #cba6f7;
                --red: #f38ba8;
                --maroon: #eba0ac;
                --peach: #fab387;
                --yellow: #f9e2af;
                --green: #a6e3a1;
                --teal: #94e2d5;
                --sky: #89dceb;
                --sapphire: #74c7ec;
                --blue: #89b4fa;
                --lavender: #b4befe;

                /* Background / Foreground Colors */
                --text: #cdd6f4;
                --subtext1: #bac2de;
                --subtext0: #a6adc8;
                --overlay2: #9399b2;
                --overlay1: #7f849c;
                --overlay0: #6c7086;
                --surface2: #585b70;
                --surface1: #45475a;
                --surface0: #313244;
                --base: #1e1e2e;
                --mantle: #181825;
                --crust: #11111b;
            }
        }
    }

    /* Space Tokens */
    @layer base {
        :root {
            --step--5: clamp(0.3686rem, 0.6197rem + -0.324vw, 0.5549rem);
            --step--4: clamp(0.4608rem, 0.6812rem + -0.2843vw, 0.6243rem);
            --step--3: clamp(0.576rem, 0.7463rem + -0.2197vw, 0.7023rem);
            --step--2: clamp(0.72rem, 0.8145rem + -0.122vw, 0.7901rem);
            --step--1: clamp(0.8889rem, 0.885rem + 0.0193vw, 0.9rem);
            --step-0: clamp(1rem, 0.9565rem + 0.2174vw, 1.125rem);
            --step-1: clamp(1.125rem, 1.0272rem + 0.4891vw, 1.4063rem);
            --step-2: clamp(1.2656rem, 1.0944rem + 0.856vw, 1.7578rem);
            --step-3: clamp(1.4238rem, 1.1548rem + 1.3451vw, 2.1973rem);
            --step-4: clamp(1.6018rem, 1.2036rem + 1.9909vw, 2.7466rem);
            --step-5: clamp(1.802rem, 1.2347rem + 2.8369vw, 3.4332rem);
            --step-6: clamp(2.0273rem, 1.2397rem + 3.9378vw, 4.2915rem);
            --step-7: clamp(2.2807rem, 1.2081rem + 5.363vw, 5.3644rem);
            --step-8: clamp(2.5658rem, 1.1259rem + 7.1995vw, 6.7055rem);

            --space-3xs: clamp(0.25rem, 0.2283rem + 0.1087vw, 0.3125rem);
            --space-2xs: clamp(0.5rem, 0.4783rem + 0.1087vw, 0.5625rem);
            --space-xs: clamp(0.75rem, 0.7065rem + 0.2174vw, 0.875rem);
            --space-s: clamp(1rem, 0.9565rem + 0.2174vw, 1.125rem);
            --space-m: clamp(1.5rem, 1.4348rem + 0.3261vw, 1.6875rem);
            --space-l: clamp(2rem, 1.913rem + 0.4348vw, 2.25rem);
            --space-xl: clamp(3rem, 2.8696rem + 0.6522vw, 3.375rem);
            --space-2xl: clamp(4rem, 3.8261rem + 0.8696vw, 4.5rem);
            --space-3xl: clamp(6rem, 5.7391rem + 1.3043vw, 6.75rem);


            /**
        $baseLineHeight: 2.5;
$baseFontSize: 62.5%;
         */
            /* Flow Spacing */
            --flow-space: var(--space-s);
            --flow-space--medium: var(--space-xl);
            --flow-space--large: var(--space-2xl);

            --base-line-height: 2.5;
            --base-font-size: 62.5%;
        }
    }

    .content-flow > * + * {
        margin-block-start: var(--flow-space);
    }

    .content-flow > * + :is(h1, h2, h3) {
        margin-block-start: var(--flow-space--large);
    }

    .content-flow > * + .has-medium-flow-space,
    .content-flow > .has-medium-flow-space + * {
        margin-block-start: var(--flow-space--medium);
    }

    .content-flow > * + .has-large-flow-space,
    .content-flow > .has-large-flow-space + * {
        margin-block-start: var(--flow-space--large);
    }


    .left {
        text-align: left;
    }

    .right {
        text-align: right;
    }

    body > div > section {
        --box-border-color: white;
        --box-rounded-radius: 8px;
        --box-border-width: 1px;
        --box-double-border-width: 1px;
    }

    .wrapper > .header {
        padding: 0 2ch 0 2ch;
    }

    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(var(--item-width, 260px), 100%), 1fr));
        grid-template-rows: masonry;
        grid-auto-flow: dense; /* Optional, but recommended */
        gap: var(--gap, 2ch);
    }

    #content, .header {
        padding: 0 2ch 2ch 2ch;
    }

    .grid-item {
        grid-row-end: var(--row-span, span 0);

        & .icon {
            img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                object-fit: contain;
                padding: 1ch 8ch;
                filter: invert(1);
            }
        }
    }

    img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
        .grid {
            width: 90%;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            grid-auto-rows: auto
        }

        .grid-item {
            grid-row-end: auto
        }
    }

    h2 {
        text-box: trim-start cap alphabetic;
    }
    .wrapper > .header > h2 {
        margin-bottom: 0.5lh;
    }

    pre > span {
        color: var(--rosewater);
    }

    .consultation {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        align-self:  flex-end;
    }


</style>

